name: Inu.
description: INU stands out as the original and first ever $INU memecoin in crypto. Unlike other tokens that use "inu" as a suffix, this token is the first to use INU as a standalone name. It was fair-launched on the Ethereum blockchain in 2022 during the depths of a bear market. The motto is simple: "ONE TOKEN. ONE FOCUS." Unlike other ecosystems that may fragment attention across multiple tokens, everything in INU revolves around a single asset. This promotes unity, deters division, and provides a singular purpose.
